{"tid":791882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然之間諗到一個好型嘅term","createTime":"2018-08-24T06:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T08:07:30.000Z","uid":191338,"like":2,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"73e1b02c347c1b9d329381518d2debd787965a33","tid":791882,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呀叔．魂</span></span></strong><br />\n簡稱A suk wan<br />\n巴士呀叔都係asw嘅典型例子<br />\n有壓力有唔岩嘅事要爆就爆，絕不啞忍吞聲不姑息養奸<br />\n豆腐火腩呢啲咁精刁細啄嘅浪漫細膩情懷都係asw嘅表現<br />\n燦神係充滿asw智慧嘅象徵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/144646_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F144646_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f3595ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/144524_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F144524_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=27ecb5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/145526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F145526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=60326f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">呀叔．暈</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/144750_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F144750_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=089141f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港呢個彈丸之地<br />\n住左一群充滿asw嘅大叔<br />\n韓星? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佬味? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n擁有豐富閱歷同人生哲理嘅大叔<br />\n先至係連登仔學習嘅好榜樣"},{"pid":"446e59230b14d75b95b7048545d029e4b433f9f9","tid":791882,"uid":136334,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/145948_0fd677b8e9d996e3f0b372d7f0e4c221.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F145948_0fd677b8e9d996e3f0b372d7f0e4c221.png&h=a0d81efc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f5f249adb4de949cc6c1d2bccce6356861ead94","tid":791882,"uid":52221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a4af85a359c3d09acf2859cbdf7e9622a5d8cc","tid":791882,"uid":10609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"同即刻駁嘴有得揮"},{"pid":"b6510b73c507243cd746819a8b1fc4361ec22d09","tid":791882,"uid":129413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"做咩啫你"},{"pid":"73a0214b2bb4c03d6815ac52a135ad09cceaf0c6","tid":791882,"uid":191338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f5f249adb4de949cc6c1d2bccce6356861ead94","tid":791882,"uid":52221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/150049_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F150049_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=69fbc6d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75c